{"tid":1076351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「不可以擁有一切」 專家警告梅根不改變恐影響英國君主制存亡","createTime":"2019-03-24T19:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-25T02:31:20.000Z","uid":41818,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"75213b0c06c812a4f76d25b02ce869a52260fe95","tid":1076351,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T19:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190323/large/1553333325_9b67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190323%2Flarge%2F1553333325_9b67.jpg&h=9a860990&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國薩塞斯克公爵夫人梅根自從上年嫁入皇室後負面新聞多多，熟悉皇室事務的作家巴斯頓納克（Anna Pasternak）批評梅根太貪心，「梅根不可以擁有一切，不可以又像明星般生活，但又享有皇室特權」，更指梅根要明白這點，否則可影響英國君主制度的存亡。<br />\n<br />\n皇室小說《Untitled: The Real Wallace Simpson, The Duchess of Windsor》的作者巴斯頓納克指出，梅根必定要明白，她不可以「以荷里活巨星」的態度生活，因為在皇室的制度裏，人人都要跟從一套獨有的規矩，「你不可以擁有一切，不可以有自由，同時又享受皇室成員的特權&hellip;&hellip;這裏不是童話故事。要認清這點，接受其後果」。<br />\n<br />\n巴斯頓納克又批評梅根上月在紐約高調舉行的產前派對「品味很差」，她說：「當國家處於一個極緊張、不穩定的狀態，而且財政緊絀的時期，我覺得你不可以兩者兼得。你不可以在一方面對人講『救救地球，節省塑膠』，但另一面又坐私人飛機，留下一大串碳足迹，就是為了去紐約辦一個產前派對。我不覺得這樣留下好印象，也不覺得這個恰當。」<br />\n<br />\n她認為梅根未明白自己在皇室制度裏的位置，以致搶走了重要皇室成員的風彩，強調受到關注的人「不是她，而是女皇和繼承人」。她續指：「我不認為她知道自己不可以是國際舞台上的巨星。這裏有女皇、查理斯、然後是威廉和凱蒂，他們注定要做矚目的巨星，這是為了讓皇室持續運作下去，歐洲大部份皇室都倒台，但溫莎王朝仍然鞏固，是因為他們明白君主必須是主角。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190324/59400965\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190324%2F59400965&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6Vtn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=3a55be33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190324%2F59400965&h=9e090a7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190324/59400965</a>"},{"pid":"6f10b9c046ab12a22157306aee3b981b8f49f0c4","tid":1076351,"uid":35430,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T19:06:32.000Z","msg":"皇室墜落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4f3af759f9f8502f58cfede109bc91d1f5512e","tid":1076351,"uid":59570,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T22:32:58.000Z","msg":"其實講得冇錯，<br />\n<br />\n皇室應該作為人民既榜樣<br />\n<br />\n而唔係挑起消費主義既慾望"},{"pid":"1d31cdbf22c9fe6964cd6cc50b893128db69efa0","tid":1076351,"uid":6030,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T23:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4j6753p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4j6753p.png&h=61862291&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9b6376d99490f18d76ea8300ade13583517c8dc","tid":1076351,"uid":165773,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T00:43:28.000Z","msg":"遲早又撞車死"},{"pid":"0067cd7b257f7727e1697cabca6eb62ec0cec7b3","tid":1076351,"uid":19501,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T00:47:28.000Z","msg":"個婚禮已經得啖笑啦"},{"pid":"264c1b25d0f913d0eabfee9696e144a73ca4b256","tid":1076351,"uid":22679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T00:51:29.000Z","msg":"佢啲taste真係差到嘔"},{"pid":"fa528cfc31074124673313f20d72f55e74b7276b","tid":1076351,"uid":238189,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T01:30:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OVk1rMq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOVk1rMq.png&h=9bde6b4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b35c9e36c549e7ca11df446c40c7afb337f91fb","tid":1076351,"uid":57376,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T02:19:50.000Z","msg":"哩個女人絕對係皇室浩劫<br />\n遲早搞到兩兄弟感情都差埋<br />\n佢個格仲要似足宮廷劇入面啲搞屎棍八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1d0f471a5312ff3